WEBVTT

1
00:20:57.200 --> 00:20:59.120 
就好像我已经死了一样
like vultures, as if I'm already dead,

2
00:21:00.070 --> 00:21:03.200 
但我们还有很多事情要做 亨利
but there's so much more still to do, Henri.

3
00:21:04.640 --> 00:21:06.570 
这...
This, uh...

4
00:21:06.570 --> 00:21:08.640 
这位美国人 杰克逊·波洛克
This American fellow, Jackson Pollock.

5
00:21:08.640 --> 00:21:10.580 
创造了新的艺术价值
He has set the art world on fire.

6
00:21:10.580 --> 00:21:12.980 
油漆画在画布上
Paint splattered on canvas.

7
00:21:12.980 --> 00:21:15.110 
为了抽象而抽象
Abstraction for the sake of abstraction.

8
00:21:15.120 --> 00:21:17.960 
我也没法理解它
I can't say I understand it either,

9
00:21:17.960 --> 00:21:20.470 
但一开始就没有人理解我用的颜色
but nobody understood my colors

10
00:21:20.480 --> 00:21:23.960 
立方主义 或是拼贴
at first, or Cubism, or collage.

11
00:21:24.420 --> 00:21:29.000 
也许波洛克发现了 我们没有或者不能做的东西
Maybe this Pollock sees something we don't, or can't.

